title: Ivern is broken beyond belief? 266k true damage dealt?! Soloq monster!!
body: Honestly not really sure how to make an image appear so click the link.

replies.body: I know this is M&G, but that damage comes in really handy whenever there's an event with a mission to deal damage. You just queue for co-op vs AI, pick Ivern, and power farm the hell out of the jungle.
Huh. So his passive is just a 6k damage execute, probably. Good to know.

Looks like that range buff really paid off huh
